channel.title: Moparscape problems
channel.description:
Okay, big problemo.
I get on hamachi, enter the network name and password for megascape 35, but when i go on moparscape, click file>new server and enter the ip, it doesn't do anything, it just says "retrying in <x> seconds"*.
Help?
*<X> meaning any number that the timer has gotten to[br][size=1]Posted at: July 27, 2006, 01:59:04 PM[/size][hr]Okay, I've decided it's not a problem with Hamachi at all.
Apparently, it won't download the cache or something like that... And by the way, this is a picture of what IMMEDIATELY comes up after I press the runMoparscape.bat and it loads.
[img]http://img156.imageshack.us/my.php?image=moparscapeproblemqf1.png[/img]
